ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectBirdtail Sioux First Nation (Manitoba) ** Creation **
PrecisOrder setting apart 3.57 hectares (8.81 acres) of land, for the use and benefit of the Birdtail Sioux First Nation as BIRDTAIL SIOUX DAKOTA NATION INDIAN RESERVE 57 C, located in the village of Foxwarren, within the rural municipality of Birtle, at approximately 146 kilometres from the City of Brandon and 320 kilometres from the City of Winnipeg, Manitoba.
